msgid "This guide explains how to implement a custom service registrar for https://smallrye.io/smallrye-stork[SmallRye Stork] and use it to programmatically register service instances at startup."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
msgid "If you are new to Stork, please read the xref:stork.adoc[Stork Getting Started Guide]."
msgstr ""

